The Six Edge Halo series places six angular halos around the pear perimeter, adding geometric edge contrast that the traditional round halo does not deliver. Available in all three major metal colors. The hidden halo sits flush beneath the stone, visible only from certain angles — the more subtle and bridal-adjacent option of the two.

