## Drop & Dangle Pear Diamond Earrings

Drop earrings suspend the pear diamond below the earlobe, point-down, where the teardrop shape reads as a natural pendant from the ear. These are the style most associated with high-fashion and formal occasions. The pear's elongation creates visual length at the jawline that round brilliant drops cannot replicate.

