## The 1 Carat Per Ear Standard

Buyers searching for **1 carat pear shaped diamond earrings**, **2 carat pear shaped diamond earrings**, and **3 carat pear shaped diamond earrings** are almost always expressing a per-ear size desire. Here is the complete guide to what each popular carat goal actually costs:

**0.50 ct per ear (1 CTW total):**
